0frontiers%20of%20technology%20to%20create%20electronic%20products%20that%20are%20so%20well-crafted%20and%20aspirational%20that%20die-hard%20fans%20turn%20sidewalks%20near%20Apple%20stores%20into%20campsites%20ahead%20of%20new%20product%20arrivals.%20They%20have%20catapulted%20it%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20with%20a%20market%20capitalisation%20of%20%243.5%20trillion%2C%20the%20same%20as%20India's%20GDP%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECook's%20visit%20is%20intriguing%20and%20important%20because%20Apple%20is%20an%20American%20native.%20And%20the%20US-China%20rivalry%2C%20especially%20in%20cutting-edge%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20is%20irrevocably%20shaping%20the%2021st%20century.%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20China's%20Minister%20of%20Industry%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Jin%20Zhuanglong%20asking%20Cook%20to%20invest%20in%20innovation%2C%20a%20sensitive%20subject%20in%20Washington%2C%20which%20wants%20to%20slow%20Beijing's%20tech%20march.%20The%20superpower%20competition%20is%20so%20intense%20that%20analysts%20sometimes%20speculate%20that%20it%20could%20spiral%20into%20war.%20Yet%2C%20the%20Apple%20chief%20vowed%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccontinue%20to%20grow%20its%20investments%20in%20China%20and%20help%20the%20high-quality%20development%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20Remains%20Un-Bypassable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20overtures%20show%20how%20China%2C%20unlike%20India%2C%20remains%20an%20un-bypassable%20economy%20for%20global%20corporations.%20Which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20Apple%20that%20is%20wooing%20China%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20round.%20How%20the%20latter%20built%20itself%20up%20into%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20hub%20is%20well-documented%20and%20India%20is%20trying%20to%20emulate%20it%20in%20its%20own%20way.%20However%2C%20its%20ability%20to%20leverage%20market%20and%20production%20capacity%20access%20to%20learn%20and%20grow%20with%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20is%20severely%20limited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Cook%20considered%20China%20so%20important%2C%20both%20as%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20and%20market%2C%20that%20the%20company%20signed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theinformation.com%2Farticles%2Ffacing-hostile-chinese-authorities-apple-ceo-signed-275-billion-deal-with-them%5C%22%3Esecret%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016%20to%20invest%20%24275%20billion%20locally%2C%20including%20billion-dollar%20infusions%20in%20Chinese%20startups%20such%20as%20Didi.%20The%20Chinese%20government%20barely%20gave%20any%20concessions%20as%20Apple%20was%20fighting%20off%20a%20regulatory%20onslaught%20with%20the%20olive%20branch%20of%20investment.%20The%20pact%20was%20an%20unqualified%20success.%20Apple%20raked%20in%20the%20moolah%20as%20it%20rode%20the%20country's%20economic%20boom%20and%20citizens'%20prosperity.%20It%20became%20the%20phonemaker's%20largest%20market%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessofapps.com%2Fdata%2Fapple-statistics%2F%5C%22%3Ebringing%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24378%20billion%20in%20revenues%20between%202016%20and%202022%20even%20as%20it%20helped%20Chinese%20companies%20upgrade%20their%20technological%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20India%20bent%20over%20backwards%20to%20woo%20iPhone%20and%20iPad%20makers%20to%20set%20up%20shop%20here.%20It%20slashed%20import%20duties%20on%20components%20while%20keeping%20out%20finished%20products%20with%20high%20levies.%20This%20has%20now%20led%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20an%20iPhone%20made%20in%20India%20is%20cheaper%20in%20Dubai%20compared%20to%20Delhi.%20An%20iPhone%2016%20with%20a%20memory%20of%20128GB%20costs%20about%20Rs%2078%2C000%20in%20a%20Dubai%20Mal%2C%20%C2%A0while%20it%20costs%20Rs%2089%2C000%20at%20the%20shiny%20Apple%20retail%20store%20in%20Delhi%20that%20Cook%20personally%20flew%20down%20to%20last%20year%20and%20flagged%20off.%20It%20took%20no%20time%20for%20the%20arbitrage%20to%20spawn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdelhi-customs-seize-26-iphone-16-pro-max-worth-rs-40-lakh-from-woman-passenger-wrapped-in-tissue-at-igi-airport%2Farticleshow%2F113869872.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esmuggling%3C%2Fa%3E%20racket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Tortuous%20Duty%20Structures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EiPhone%20smuggling%20may%20not%20cause%20much%20damage%20to%20the%20exchequer%2C%20but%20warped%20duty%20structures%20and%20perverse%20incentives%20distort%20the%20market%20so%20much%20that%20larger%20national%20objectives%20and%20development%20agenda%20are%20crumbling.%20Protectionist%20tariffs%20have%20stunted%20the%20growth%20and%20innovation%20in%20the%20solar%20industry.%20As%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarboncopy.info%2Fprice-surge-or-power-surge-indias-solar-conundrum%2F%5C%22%3Ethree-part%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%2C%20India's%20renewable%20energy%20programme%20is%20weighing%20heavily%20on%20the%20finances%20of%20electricity%20distribution%20companies%2C%20ordinary%20consumers%2C%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20taxpayers.%20State-owned%20public%20distribution%20companies%20have%20accumulated%20losses%20of%20Rs%206.77%20lakh%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20solar%20energy%20firms%20find%20it%20more%20profitable%20to%20import%20photovoltaic%20cells%20from%20China%20and%20assemble%20modules%20to%20ship%20to%20other%20markets%20as%20well%20as%20sell%20to%20local%20users.%20High%20import%20duties%20on%20modules%20but%20low%20levies%20on%20cells%20ensure%20wide%20margins%20for%20module%20makers%20and%20high%20costs%20for%20power%20distributors%20and%20end%20consumers.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ERelying%20On%20Just%20Arbitrage%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20policies%20also%20have%20wider%2C%20unintended%20consequences.%20For%20instance%2C%20small%20manufacturers%20(read%20assemblers)%20use%20imported%20Chinese%20components%20in%20white-labelled%20goods%20and%20own%20brands%20to%20sell%20in%20regional%20markets.%20One%20such%20Maharashtra-based%20entrepreneur%20with%20a%20topline%20of%20about%20Rs%2075%20crore%20says%20that%20his%20products%20enjoy%20good%20margins%20and%20give%20bigger%20companies%20a%20run%20for%20their%20money.%20He%20keeps%20costs%20low%20by%20managing%20sales%2C%20operations%2C%20procurement%20and%20logistics%2C%20all%20by%20himself.%20Levies%20are%20fickle%20and%20an%20upward%20revision%20will%20squeeze%20margins%20and%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20risk%20raising%20costs%20by%20hiring%20specialists.%20That%20means%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20success%20is%20neither%20technological%20innovation%20nor%20organisational%20efficiency%20but%20arbitrage.%20It%20also%20means%20the%20duty%20structure%20intended%20to%20boost%20local%20manufacturing%20and%20job%20creation%20is%20merely%20promoting%20product%20assembly%20while%20generating%20few%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Tata%20Group-owned%20plant%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20that%20makes%20back%20panels%20for%20older%20models%20of%20the%20iPhone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fapple-may-need-to-turn-to-china-after-tata-plant-fire-report-12833626.html%5C%22%3Ecaught%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20unit%20is%20the%20only%20producer%20of%20the%20critical%20component%2C%20forcing%20iPhone%20maker%20Foxconn%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Tata%20Group%20(it%20assembles%20older%20models%20at%20another%20unit)%20to%20source%20the%20parts%20from%20China%20to%20meet%20global%20demand%20in%20peak%20festival%20season.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereports%20that%20business%20was%20a%20key%20factor%20even%20in%20achieving%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20India-China%20border%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20China%20Is%20Pacing%20Ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Cook%20signed%20the%20secret%20deal%20in%202016%2C%20Apple%20vowed%20to%20localise%20component%20sourcing%20and%20stitch%20up%20deals%20with%20Chinese%20software%20firms%2C%20collaborate%20on%20technology%20with%20Chinese%20universities%20and%20directly%20invest%20in%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20until%202022.%20It%20also%20committed%20to%20building%20research%20and%20development%20centres%20and%20renewable%20energy%20projects%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Information%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Apple%20was%20not%20the%20only%20US%20company%20to%20sign%20such%20a%20deal.%20Microsoft%20and%20Cisco%20signed%20similar%20deals%20that%20helped%20local%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20innovation.%20The%20ecosystem%20they%20helped%20build%20no%20doubt%20contributed%20to%20bolstering%20the%20technological%20prowess%20of%20Chinese%20manufacturing.%20But%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20homegrown%20companies%20also%20developed%20their%20own%20expertise%20and%20breakthroughs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20scientists%20have%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pv-magazine.com%2F2023%2F01%2F02%2Fnew-electrolyzer-to-split-saltwater-into-hydrogen%2F%5C%22%3Ebuilt%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20electrolyzer%20that%20can%20directly%20split%20seawater%20to%20produce%20hydrogen.%20A%20Beijing-based%20energy%20startup%20Betavolt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.world-nuclear-news.org%2FArticles%2FNuclear-battery-Chinese-firm-aiming-for-mass-mark%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20this%20year%20that%20it%20had%20built%20a%20commercially%20viable%20coin-sized%20nuclear%20battery%20that%20can%20power%20a%20mobile%20phone%20for%2050%20years.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20number%20of%20SMEs%20producing%20new%20and%20unique%20products%20using%20special%20and%20sophisticated%20technologies%20exceeded%2070%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Report%20on%20the%20Work%20of%20the%20Government%20presented%20at%20the%2014th%20National%20People's%20Congress.%20To%20compare%2C%20the%20number%20of%20technology%20SMEs%20in%20India%20is%20just%20over%2010%2C000%2C%20as%20per%20Nasscom.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20in%20software%20and%20do%20work%20for%20larger%20firms.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20no%20Indian%20companies%20doing%20advanced%20research%20and%20innovation.%20But%20they%20are%20few%20and%20far%20between%2C%20and%20are%20often%20starved%20of%20capital.%20Tata%20Sons%20at%20207%20is%20the%20only%20Indian%20company%20in%20the%202024%20Patent%20300%20list%2C%20an%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fharrityllp.com%2Fpatent300%2F%5C%22%3Eglobal%20ranking%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20innovators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Firms%20Need%20To%20Value%20Innovation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20offers%20liberal%20tax%20incentives%20to%20manufacturing%20companies%20and%20SMEs%20if%20they%20invest%20in%20R%26amp%3BD.%20India%2C%20too%2C%20offers%20tax%20breaks%20up%20to%20150%25%2C%20but%20it's%20mainly%20used%20by%20Global%20Capacity%20Centres%20(GCC)%20of%20foreign%20companies%20because%20even%20large%20Indian%20firms%20rarely%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20innovation.%20The%20R%26amp%3BD%20tax%20break%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20availability%20of%20cheap%2C%20high-quality%20talent%2C%20for%20the%20mushrooming%20of%20GCCs%20(over%201%2C600%20now)%20in%20India.%20The%20knowledge%20and%20patents%20created%2C%20however%2C%20do%20not%20belong%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20planning%20often%20tends%20to%20be%20short-termist.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20holistically%20reassess%20its%20incentive%20structures%20to%20make%20the%20local%20industry%20truly%20independent%20and%20competitive%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dinesh%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20'The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation'.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729776900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbm97gra8_apple_625x300_24_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchina-or-india-which-is-a-better-handshake-for-tim-cook-6864616%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apples%20overtures%20show%20how%20China%2C%20unlike%20India%2C%20remains%20an%20un-bypassable%20economy%20for%20global%20corporations.%20Which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20Apple%20that%20is%20wooing%20China%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20round.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar's%20Grandnephew%20To%20Contest%20Against%20Ajit%20Pawar%20In%20Baramati%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar's%20grandnephew%20Yugendra%20Pawar%20to%20contest%20against%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20Baramati%20in%20Maharashtra%20election%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729776720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Flrogfps4_ajit-pawar-sharad-pawar-pti-_625x300_26_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-election-sharad-pawars-grandnephew-yugendra-pawar-to-contest-against-ajit-pawar-in-baramati-6864663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Election%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Grandnephew%20Yugendra%20Pawar%20To%20Contest%20Against%20Ajit%20Pawar%20In%20Baramati%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Machine%20Gun%20Kelly%20to%20Perform%20During%20Halftime%20at%20the%20NFL%E2%80%99s%20Giants-Panthers%20Game%20in%20Germany%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729776600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fmgk_lonelyroad2_Just-MGK-Image.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%