2canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fcant-be-a-coincidence-that-everyone-hates-meghan-markle-royal-expert%2Farticleshow%2F114551358.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fcant-be-a-coincidence-that-everyone-hates-meghan-markle-royal-expert%2Famp_articleshow%2F114551358.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fcant-be-a-coincidence-that-everyone-hates-meghan-markle-royal-expert%2Famp_articleshow%2F114551358.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI'm%201st%20Indian%20Envoy%20To%20Be%20Persona%20Non%20Grata%26quot%3B%3A%20Diplomat%20Targeted%20By%20Trudeau%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Canada%20who%20was%20targeted%20by%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20has%20since%20been%20recalled%20by%20New%20Delhi%20reiterated%20today%20that%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20was%20shared%26quot%3B%20with%20him%20by%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20who%20labelled%20him%20and%20five%20other%20diplomats%20as%20'persons%20of%20interest'%20in%20the%20murder%20investigation%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20in%20his%20first%20interview%20since%20his%20return%20to%20India%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20said%20that%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20India%20which%20had%20shared%20detailed%20evidence%20of%20radical%20and%20extremist%20groups%20operating%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20with%20the%20Justin%20Trudeau%20government%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bno%20action%20was%20taken%20on%20it%26quot%3B%20by%20either%20the%20government%20or%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBesides%20the%20evidence%20shared%20with%20Canada%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20through%20its%20High%20Commission%2C%20also%20repeatedly%20sent%20extradition%20requests%20for%2026%20radical%20elements%20and%20gangsters%2C%20but%20nothing%20was%20done%20about%20it%20by%20the%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20purely%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20standards%26quot%3B%20by%20Canada%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bone%20law%20applies%20to%20you%20and%20another%20law%20applies%20to%20me%2C%20that%20doesn't%20work%20in%20the%20world%20anymore.%20In%20the%20past%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20would%20do%20as%20was%20told%20to%20them%20by%20the%20developed%20nations%2C%20but%20gone%20are%20those%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOUT%20OF%20THE%20BLUE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20that%20in%20his%20last%20meeting%20with%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%2C%20it%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20him%20when%20he%20was%20informed%20by%20them%20that%20he%20and%20five%20other%20colleagues%20were%20now%20labelled%20%26quot%3Bpersons%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20murder%20investigation%20and%20that%20they%20should%20%26quot%3Bask%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20remove%20their%20diplomatic%20immunity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20my%20tenure%20(as%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20Canada)%2C%20my%20relations%20with%20all%20the%20ministries%20and%20with%20interlocutors%20were%20very%20cordial%2C%20But%20on%20October%2012%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Canadian%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20I%20was%20informed%20that%20six%20of%20us%20were%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20murder%20investigation%20and%20for%20them%20to%20interrogate%20us%2C%20our%20diplomatic%20immunity%20has%20to%20be%20removed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20was%20going%20too%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20communicated%20this%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20then%20decided%20to%20recall%20him%20and%20the%20other%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'DECLARED%20PERSONA%20NON%20GRATA'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20withdrew%20us%2C%20they%20(Canadian%20government)%20decided%20to%20label%20us%20as%20'persona%20non%20grata'%20and%20be%20sent%20packing%20within%20a%20given%20timeline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India's%20diplomatic%20history%20that%20any%20foreign%20ministry%20official%20or%20representative%20has%20been%20labeled%20a%20persona%20non%20grata%2C%20which%20means%20a%20person%20who%20is%20no%20longer%20welcomed%2C%20and%20in%20diplomacy%2C%20if%20the%20person%20concerned%20is%20not%20recalled%20by%20the%20home%20country%20as%20requested%2C%20the%20host%20state%20may%20refuse%20to%20recognize%20the%20person%20concerned%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20mission%20-%20meaning%20their%20immunity%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20is%20considered%20a%20friendly%20country%20to%20India%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20we%20have%20had%20known%20differences%20for%20decades%2C%20the%20last%20high%20commissioner%20to%20be%20recalled%20by%20New%20Delhi%2C%20my%20predecessor%20in%20Canada%2C%20Mr%20Ajay%20Bisaria%2C%20he%20remained%20a%20high%20commissioner%20who%20was%20called%20back%20and%20remained%20the%20then%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20even%20though%20he%20stopped%20residing%20in%20Pakistan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'TRUDEAU'S%20CLAIMS%20WON'T%20STAND%20IN%20COURT'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20has%20been%20shared%20with%20us%20(India).%20If%20they%20are%20calling%20intelligence%20inputs%20or%20source-based%20claims%20as%20'evidence'%2C%20then%20that%20will%20not%20stand%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%20-%20not%20in%20their%20country%2C%20nor%20in%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20or%20RCMP%20said%2C%20and%20something%20that%20Trudeau%20said%20as%20well%20during%20his%20deposition%20to%20the%20court%20of%20inquiry%20on%20foreign%20interference%2C%20was%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20proof%20or%20evidence%2C%20but%20rather%20intelligence%20inputs%20from%20sources%20-%20which%20is%20just%20hearsay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20quite%20funny%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Verma%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20they%20have%20done%20is%20actually%20quite%20serious.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20understand%20most%20of%20the%20things%20they%20are%20calling%20evidence%20is%20just%20hearsay%20and%20source-based%20claims%2C%20and%20let's%20not%20forget%20that%20there%20are%20many%20India%20baiters%20there%20who%20are%20ready%20to%20give%20false%20statements%20against%20India%20or%20Indians%2C%20which%20could%20then%20be%20considered%20single%20sourced%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECOLLECTING%20INFORMATION%20-%20JOB%20OF%20A%20DIPLOMAT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollecting%20information%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20a%20diplomats%20job.%20Explaining%20this%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20break%20this%20down%20for%20you.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20in%20which%20information%20is%20collected%20by%20a%20diplomat%20-%20an%20overt%20way%2C%20which%20is%20through%20the%20open%20source%2C%20and%20a%20covert%20way.%20I%20can%20confirm%20to%20you%20here%20that%20yes%2C%20we%20depended%20on%20the%20information%20we%20got%20through%20open%20sources%20-%20the%20overt%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20collect%20information%20about%20banned%20organisations%2C%20radicals%2C%20extremists%2C%20etc%20from%20what%20is%20available%20through%20the%20news%2C%20through%20social%20media.%20So%20we%20did%20that%2C%20and%20we%20did%20the%20analysis%20based%20on%20the%20credible%20information%20we%20collected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20trend%20seen%20in%20the%20analysis%20we%20made%20was%20very%20clear.%20They%20want%20to%20sabotage%20and%20destroy%20Canada%20India%20relations.%20They%20want%20India's%20image%20to%20be%20maligned%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'JUSTIN%20TRUDEAU%20PERSONALLY%20INVOLVED'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20is%20quite%20openly%20seen%20and%20known%20-%20that%20Mr%20Trudeau%20himself%20is%20known%20to%20be%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Khalistani%20extremists%20and%20terrorists%2C%20especially%20politically.%20Through%20his%20close%20circles%2C%20both%20in%20his%20cabinet%20and%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament%2C%20some%20of%20his%20close%20friends%20are%20not%20quite%20inclined%20towards%20good%20Canada-India%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20domestic%20politics%20in%20Canada%2C%20but%20what%20I%20have%20seen%2C%20heard%20and%20read%20in%20the%20media%2C%20is%20that%20his%20party%20is%20not%20doing%20well.%20The%20opinion%20polls%20are%20not%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20and%20most%20of%20all%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20leadership%20is%20threatened%20even%20within%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729776360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F47o5fu18_recalled-high-commissioner-to-canada-sanjay-kumar-verma-ndtv_625x300_24_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnot-a-shred-of-evidence-shared-with-us-indian-envoy-targeted-by-trudeau-6863897%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Canada%20who%20was%20targeted%20by%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20has%20since%20been%20recalled%20by%20New%20Delhi%20reiterated%20today%20that%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20was%20shared%26quot%3B%20with%20him%20by%20the%20Canadian%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unilever%20chief%20says%20it%20is%20determined%20to%20grow%20its%20food%20business%