-and-coming%20payments%20startup%20challenging%20Stripe%20and%20Square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinix%2C%20founded%20in%202016%2C%20lets%20other%20businesses%20accept%2C%20disburse%2C%20and%20manage%20payments.%20The%20San%20Francisco-based%20startup%20raised%20%2475%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20Thursday.%20The%20round%20included%20Acrew%20Capital%20and%20Lightspeed%20Venture%20Partners%2C%20which%20have%20invested%20in%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20fintechs%2C%20like%20Chime%20and%20Coinbase%2C%20and%20Affirm%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinix%2C%20which%20has%20raised%20%24208%20million%20to%20date%2C%20was%20named%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F49-most-promising-fintech-startups-according-top-vc-investors-2024%23finix-23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20most%20promising%20fintechs%20of%202024%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20main%20selling%20point%20is%20helping%20companies%2C%20with%20little-to-no%20technical%20resources%2C%20facilitate%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20a%20coffee%20shop%20accepting%20a%20payment%20from%20a%20customer%2C%20an%20artist%20selling%20their%20painting%20on%20a%20digital%20marketplace%20like%20Etsy%2C%20or%20an%20airline%20refunding%20a%20customer%20for%20lost%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20if%20a%20business%20wanted%20to%20handle%20different%20kinds%20of%20payments%2C%20it'd%20need%20to%20use%20different%20providers%20and%20manage%20the%20multiple%20integrations%20that%20would%20come%20with%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Finix%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%2C%20Richie%20Serna.%20Finix%20is%20trying%20to%20change%20that%20by%20facilitating%20in-store%20and%20online%20payments%2C%20accepting%20payments%20and%20disbursing%20payouts%2C%20handling%20payments%20between%20different%20countries%2C%20and%20serving%20subscription%20software%20companies%20that%20need%20to%20enable%20payments%20between%20multiple%20merchants%20and%20multiple%20customers%2C%20like%20Airbnb%20or%20Uber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinix%20processes%20billions%20of%20dollars%20every%20month%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20merchants%2C%20Serna%20said.%20In%20the%20last%20year%2C%20the%20startup%20quadrupled%20its%20revenue%2C%20he%20added.%20He%20declined%20to%20disclose%20Finix's%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a8d6dbf-ac43-4982-8e23-213cb547eb27%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinix%20leans%20into%20low%20code%2C%20no%20code%20tools%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinix%20mostly%20targets%20companies%20that%20lack%20the%20software-developer%20resources%20to%20set%20up%20and%20customize%20their%20payments%20offerings.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20its%20value%20proposition%20is%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-low-code-no-code-startups-investors-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Blow%20code%2C%20no%20code%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20tools%20that%20help%20non-programmers%20build%20apps%20and%20automate%20simple%20tasks%20without%20needing%20to%20know%20how%20to%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Adyen's%20for%20the%20enterprise%2C%20Square's%20for%20the%20micro-merchant%2C%20Stripe%20is%20for%20the%20developer-centric%20startup%2C%20Finix%20is%20for%20the%2022%20million%20businesses%20that%20don't%20have%20developers%20or%20don't%20have%20enough%20developers%2C%26quot%3B%20Serna%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarving%20out%20that%20slice%20of%20market%20share%20hasn't%20stopped%20Finix%20from%20competing%20with%20those%20larger%20payments%20players%2C%20though.%20Sales%20call%20data%20with%20prospective%20customers%20show%20that%20Finix%20is%20up%20against%20Stripe%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20time%2C%20Serna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20win%2060%25%20of%20the%20deals%20that%20we%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20deals%20in%20Finix's%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerna%20previously%20was%20an%20engineer%20at%20Balanced%2C%20a%20now-defunct%20payments%20company%20that%2C%20when%20forced%20to%20shutter%20its%20operations%20in%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2015%2F03%2F13%2Fbalanced-is-closing-its-marketplace-payment-platform-in-90-days-strikes-transition-deal-with-rival-stripe%2F%3Fguccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAAD9AUTOZ4UGQtsgzWBHTSufCBvXT5DykBmX6CR4dPwvYJvEKieoV_OHCvHOzLijdi9sqnutK347daY5o0pWMsniKGNi_-UeyOuFFaNNcCUfBY-qsIyIKWQmvljUidJLRY3thAQDr1fFjkGkjrOJ7akXgmFl0wI0S7QyfxAldQ2O9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20a%20deal%20with%20its%20longtime%20rival%2C%20Stripe%2C%20to%20transition%20existing%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efe8a21f-1168-4017-8943-45f0eebd9382%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Six%20to%2010%20companies%20that%20are%20smashed%20together'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20Finix%20comes%20up%20against%20Stripe%20and%20other%20payment%20processors%20could%20be%20because%20the%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20offer%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20for%20various%20payments%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinix%20is%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20six%20to%2010%20companies%20that%20are%20smashed%20together%20and%20have%20to%20work%20extremely%20seamlessly%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Serna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20hood%2C%20Finix%20underwrites%20all%20new%20merchants%2C%20which%20involves%20a%20dozen%20or%20two%20different%20compliance%20checks%3B%20runs%20a%20risk%20system%20that%20uses%20machine%20learning%20to%20determine%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20person%20paying%3B%20stores%20credit-card%20info%20in%20a%20compliant%20and%20secure%20way%3B%20and%20facilitates%20the%20connection%20between%20the%20card%20networks%2C%20payment%20rails%2C%20and%20accounting%20systems%2C%20Serna%20said.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Finix%20layers%20APIs%2C%20front-end%20dashboards%20for%20managing%20payments%2C%20and%20check-o