20easier%20for%20those%20who%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20lives%2C%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20WeLive%20began%20when%20one%20of%20its%20founders%2C%20a%20former%20CCI%20warden%2C%20saw%20firsthand%20the%20difficulties%20young%20adults%20faced%20upon%20leaving%20institutional%20care.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20few%20of%20them%20turned%2018%2C%20he%20took%20them%20into%20his%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Ramya%20Sundararajan%2C%20CEO%20of%20WeLive%20Foundation.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20experience%20sparked%20the%20idea%20for%20WeLive.%E2%80%9D%20The%20foundation%20opened%20its%20first%20centre%20for%20young%20men%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20December%202020%2C%20with%20just%20five%20residents.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20expanded%20to%20three%20residential%20programmes%20across%20Bengaluru%20and%20Chennai%2C%20supporting%20both%20men%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Ffit%3D1233%252C822%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221233%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WeLive's%20residency%20programme%20focuses%20on%20well-being%20and%20work%20readiness%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fw%3D1233%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201233w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C333%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C512%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C800%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FChennai-Center-Launch_040_11zon-1729768067.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C100%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22822%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWeLive%E2%80%99s%20residency%20programme%20focuses%20on%20well-being%20and%20work%20readiness%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20WeLive%E2%80%99s%20residency%20programme%20are%20two%20pillars%3A%20well-being%20and%20work%20readiness%20Every%20young%20adult%20who%20joins%20WeLive%E2%80%99s%20aftercare%20residency%20programme%20is%20required%20to%20follow%20a%20structured%20path%20that%20combines%20work%20and%20education.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20resident%20must%20have%20a%20part-time%20job%20and%20be%20enrolled%20in%20a%20study%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ramya.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20those%20who%20have%20passed%20their%2010th%20grade%2C%20we%20prepare%20them%20to%20complete%20their%2012th%20through%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS).%20If%20they%E2%80%99ve%20already%20matriculated%2C%20they%20pursue%20higher%20education%20in%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20academic%20and%20professional%20development%20are%20only%20part%20of%20the%20equation.%20Ramya%20emphasises%20that%20these%20young%20adults%20often%20carry%20heavy%20emotional%20burdens.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20have%20endured%20severe%20trauma%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20function%2C%20let%20alone%20focus%20on%20work%20or%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20This%20is%20why%20WeLive%20places%20equal%20importance%20on%20its%20well-being%20pillar%2C%20which%20offers%20counselling%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231083%2Fmental-health-stress-depression-anxiety-covid-19-online-therapy-sessions-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychological%20support%2C%20and%20mentorshi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231083%2Fmental-health-stress-depression-anxiety-covid-19-online-therapy-sessions-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%3Ep%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20if%20a%20youth%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20good%20from%20within%2C%20it%20can%20be%20incredibly%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20hold%20down%20a%20job%20or%20excel%20in%20their%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramya%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018%20to%2023%2C%20these%20young%20care%20leavers%20from%20about%2010-12%20states%20of%20India%20are%20open%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20facility%20for%202-3%20years%20until%20they%20gain%20some%20work%20experience%2C%20education%20and%20savings%20to%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamya%2C%20recalling%20the%20earlier%20days%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20started%2C%20our%20focus%20was%20on%20improving%20work%20readiness.%20It%20seemed%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20the%20youth%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F272114%2Fautobot-india-academy-provides-jobs-for-electric-vehicle-engineers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskilling%20and%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20streams%2C%20and%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs.%20However%2C%20ensuring%20they%20stayed%20in%20these%20jobs%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%20Many%2C%20like%20most%20of%20us%2C%20switch%20two%20or%20three%20jobs%20before%20settling%2C%20and%20guiding%20them%20through%20this%20process%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20support.%20Once%20we%20established