2canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Ftko-acquires-pbr-img-on-location-endeavor-1236189455%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Setback%20For%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Clock%20Symbol%20Stays%20With%20Ajit%20Pawar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20clock%20symbol%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20will%20stay%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%20in%20a%20setback%20for%20veteran%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20ahead%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20election.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20added%20that%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20has%20to%20%26quot%3Bmeticulously%26quot%3B%20follow%20its%20earlier%20order%20and%20add%20disclaimers%20in%20election%20advertisements%2C%20clarifying%20that%20the%20court%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20a%20final%20decision%20in%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20feel%20that%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20is%20being%20made%20to%20violate%20our%20order%2C%20we%20can%20initiate%20suo%20motu%20contempt%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%2C%20Dipankar%20Datta%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20temporary%20order%20came%20when%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20had%20approached%20the%20top%20court%2C%20challenging%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20decision%20to%20award%20of%20the%20party%20name%20and%20election%20symbol%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction.%20It%20had%20asked%20that%20both%20factions%20be%20given%20new%20symbol%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20had%20gone%20to%20court%2C%20complaining%20that%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20flouted%20its%20order%20and%20did%20not%20add%20any%20disclaimer%20in%20its%20election%20posters%20and%20banners%2C%20creating%20%26quot%3Blarge%20scale%20confusion%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20voters%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20bench%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%2C%20directing%20that%20it%20should%20not%20create%20%26quot%3Ban%20embarrassing%20situation%26quot%3B%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20file%20a%20fresh%20undertaking%20as%20well%20that%20you%20will%20not%20violate%20our%20directions%20present%20as%20well%20as%20till%20the%20end%20of%20elections.%20We%20expect%20both%20sides%20to%20comply%20our%20directions.%20Please%20don't%20create%20an%20embarrassing%20(situation)%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20had%20founded%20the%20NCP%20with%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Purno%20Sangma%20and%20Tariq%20Anwar%20in%201999%20after%20their%20expulsion%20from%20the%20Congress.%20In%20July%20last%20year%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20-%20complaining%20about%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20leadership%20--%20had%20walked%20away%20with%20a%20majority%20of%20MLAs%20and%20supported%20the%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20government%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2015%2C%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar%20-%20in%20response%20to%20complaints%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20faction%20--%20maintained%20that%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20was%20the%20real%20NCP.%20The%20anti-defection%20law%20cannot%20be%20used%20in%20this%20case%20since%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20internal%20dissent%20and%20he%20had%20the%20numbers%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20allotted%20the%20NCP%20symbol%20'clock'%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20group%20and%20allowed%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20to%20call%20itself%20the%20%26quot%3BNationalist%20Congress%20Party-Sharadchandra%20Pawar%26quot%3B%20and%20use%20the%20%26quot%3BMan%20blowing%20Turha%26quot%3B%20as%20its%20symbol.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%2C%20founded%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20had%20'cl