ur%20diet%20as%20a%20whole%20and%20give%20you%20nutritional%20recommendations%2C%20which%20is%20important%20because%20supplements%20should%20complement%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20a%20healthy%20diet%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d95e9da7-c796-4d02-ae5c-f6a75e60847a%5C%22%3EDo%20research%20based%20on%20reputable%20sources%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can't%20get%20advice%20from%20a%20medical%20professional%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20get%20information%20from%20a%20reputable%20source%2C%20Pasiakos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20information%20everywhere.%20You%20just%20type%20in%20a%20given%20supplement%20online%20and%20you'll%20get%20everybody%20under%20the%20sun%20with%20an%20opinion%20on%20whether%20a%20dietary%20supplement%20works%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Pasiakos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ODS%20has%20lots%20of%20information%20on%20its%20website%2C%20including%20dietary%20supplement%20fact%20sheets%2C%20which%20are%20up-to-date%2C%20evidence-based%20reviews%20of%20the%20available%20information%2C%20he%20said.%20There's%20a%20fact%20sheet%20for%20most%20existing%20supplement%20ingredients%20that%20explains%20what%20it%20is%2C%20how%20it%20works%2C%20and%20the%20evidence%20for%20or%20against%20claimed%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasiakos%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Complementary%20Integrative%20Health%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20NIH%2C%20and%20the%20FDA's%20website%20as%20good%20sources%20of%20information%20on%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-supplement-experts-tips-for-buying-safe-products-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729767685000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67163923a0a0cc14f222817f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-supplement-experts-tips-for-buying-safe-products-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dietary%20supplements%20aren't%20FDA-approved%20like%20drugs.%20The%20director%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20Dietary%20Supplements%20offered%20advice%20including%20buying%20products%20that%20are%20verified%20by%20a%20third%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-supplement-experts-tips-for-buying-safe-products-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SEBI%20Chief%20Skips%20Parliament%20Panel%20Meet%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Calls%20Summons%20%26quot%3BPartisan%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESEBI%20chairperson%20Madhabi%20Puri%20Buch%20skipped%20a%20Parliament's%20Public%20Accounts%20Committee%20meeting%20on%20Thursday%2C%20prompting%20panel%20head%20KC%20Venugopal%20to%20postpone%20the%20sitting%2C%20with%20NDA%20members%20accusing%20him%20of%20taking%20unilateral%20decisions%20and%20lodging%20a%20protest%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venugopal%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20committee%20received%20a%20communication%20from%20Ms%20Buch%20at%209.30%20am%20that%20she%20and%20her%20team%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20panel%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bexigencies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20indicated%20his%20disapproval%20of%20her%20decision%20noting%20that%20Ms%20Buch%20had%20confirmed%20her%20presence%20after%20her%20earlier%20request%20for%20an%20exemption%20was%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20a%20woman's%20request%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20better%20to%20postpone%20today's%20meeting%20for%20another%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Venugopal%20said%20as%20he%20along%20with%20other%20Opposition%20members%20left%20the%20venue%20minutes%20after%20the%20meeting%20began%20amid%20sharp%20exchanges%20between%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Opposition%20member%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Buch%20informing%20the%20committee%20about%20her%20decision%20with%20less%20than%20two%20hours%20to%20go%20for%20the%20meeting%20to%20begin%20virtually%20amounts%20to%20contempt%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20members%20accused%20Mr%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20of%20not%20letting%20them%20put%20across%20their%20views.%20They%20later%20charged%20him%20with%20acting%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuo%20motu%26quot%3B%20manner%2C%20suggesting%20that%20his%20decision%20to%20summon%20Ms%20Buch%20and%20even%20some%20other%20regulatory%20bodies%20established%20by%20the%20acts%20of%20parliament%20was%20his%20own%20and%20guided%20by%20partisan%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPAC%20member%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20told%20reporters%20that%20many%20standing%20committees%20review%20the%20performance%20of%20various%20bodies%20e.g.%20the%20panel%20on%20finance%20scrutinises%20the%20work%20of%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20and%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Communication%20and%20Information%20Technology%20panel%20scrutinises%20the%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20(Mr%20Venugopal)%20own%20words%20are%20suo%20motu.%20How%20did%20you%20decide%3F%20The%20PAC's%20job%20is%20to%20consider%20CAG%20reports.%20We%20have%20this%20information%20from%20reliable%20sources%20that%20the%20CAG%20has%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20SEBI.%20This%20entire%20conduct%20is%20unparliamentary.%20The%20conduct%20of%20the%20chairperson%20in%20the%20way%20he%20adjourned%2C%20did%20not%20allow%20us%20to%20speak.%20And%20(he)%20walked%20out%20(which)%20shows%20he%20has%20extraneous%20political%20considerations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Prasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Union%20law%20minister%20said%20the%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20was%20in%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20main%20objection%20was%20how%20did%20he%20(Mr%20Venugopal)%20make%20suo%20motu%20selection%20of%20subjects%20without%20consulting%20other%20members%3F%20Nobody%20had%20an%20inkling%20of%20the%20list%20that%20was%20prepared%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Prasad%2C%20flanked%20by%20other%20NDA%20members%20of%20the%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20PAC%20secretariat%20officials%20leaving%20the%20venue%20after%20Mr%20Venugopal%20adjourned%20the%20meeting%20when%20many%20other%20members%20remained%20inside.%20The%20NDA%20members%20met%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20later%20to%20register%20their%20protest%20against%20Mr%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research's%20accusation%20of%20conflict%20of%20interest%20against%20Ms%20Buch%20over%20the%20SEBI's%20probe%20into%20the%20short-seller's%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20was%20seized%20upon%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20seek%20her%20ouster%20and%20to%20attack%20the%20government%2C%20giving%20political%20dimensions%20to%20the%20panel's%20missive%20to%20her%20to%20appear%20before%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPAC%20member%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20wrote%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20last%20month%20against%20Mr%20Venugopal%2C%20accusing%20the%20Congress%20leader%20of%20raking%20up%20%26quot%3Bnon-existent%26quot%3B%20issues%20to%20defame%20the%20central%20government%20and%20allegedly%20destabilise%20the%20country's%20financial%20structure%20and%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20Mr%20Venugopal%20of%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%20and%20disdainful%26quot%3B%20conduct%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20said%20the%20committee's%20chairperson%20actions%20are%20guided%20by%20political%20motivations%20after%20the%20Congress%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompelled%26quot%3B%20by%20voters%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20opposition%20benches%20following%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20unverified%20allegations%