ef-at-popular-ibiza-restaurant-charged-over-attack-on-customer-who-sent-back-food-13240263%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20chef%20at%20a%20popular%20Ibiza%20restaurant%20has%20been%20charged%20after%20he%20allegedly%20assaulted%20a%20German%20customer%20who%20sent%20back%20food.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchef-at-popular-ibiza-restaurant-charged-over-attack-on-customer-who-sent-back-food-13240263%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchef-at-popular-ibiza-restaurant-charged-over-attack-on-customer-who-sent-back-food-13240263%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchef-at-popular-ibiza-restaurant-charged-over-attack-on-customer-who-sent-back-food-13240263%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20At%20BRICS%20And%20The%20Curious%20Case%20Of%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fsh27snjg_brics_625x300_24_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20have%20been%20on%20Iran%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20Naturally%2C%20the%20first%20BRICS%20summit%20with%20Tehran's%20membership%20is%20bound%20to%20breed%20speculation%20about%20what%20the%20prospective%20new%20world%20order%20would%20look%20like.%20At%20home%2C%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20an%20examination%20of%20India's%20bilateral%20ties%20with%20a%20country%20that%20is%20seen%20firmly%20anti-West%20in%20its%20outlook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20and%20India%20are%20sailing%20in%20the%20same%20boat%2C%20at%20least%20momentarily%3A%20of%20the%20West's%20castigation.%20The%20temptation%20may%20be%20high%20on%20both%20sides%20to%20form%20a%20joint%20front%20against%20Western%20hegemony%20in%20the%20security%20space.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20held%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20the%20new%20Iranian%20President%2C%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20strategic%20cooperation%20in%20and%20beyond%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20Groupings%20vs%20Realpolitik%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20endlessly%20debated%20without%20inching%20anywhere%20close%20to%20a%20resolution%20whether%20multilateral%20global%20groupings%20make%20any%20difference%20to%20realpolitik%20either%20domestically%20or%20internationally.%20The%20signalling%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20crucial.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20West%20is%20already%20perceiving%20the%20summit%20as%20Russia's%20show%20of%20strength.%20Headlines%20like%20'Putin%20Gathers%20Allies'%20and%20'Putin%20Hosts%20Global%20South%20Leaders%20at%20BRICS%20Summit%20Meant%20to%20Counterbalance%20Western%20Clout'%20in%20Western%20media%20outlets%20expose%20apprehension.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20complex%20interplay%20of%20sectarian%20interests%20and%20regional%20dynamics%20shapes%20Iran's%20geopolitical%20strategy.%20It%20is%20in%20the%20direct%20line%20of%20fire%2C%20thanks%20to%20Israel's%20unchecked%20belligerence.%20Already%20reeling%20under%20economic%20pressure%20owing%20to%20the%20UN%20sanctions%20of%202011%2C%20the%20post-October%207%20reality%20for%20Tehran%20is%20even%20grimmer.%20Iran%20blames%20the%20US%20for%20almost%20all%20of%20its%20problems.%20As%20such%2C%20during%20the%20last%20summit%2C%20former%20president%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20had%20anointed%20Iran's%20proposed%20BRICS%20membership%20as%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20of%20getting%20even%20with%20the%20US%20and%20the%20West%20at%20large.%20%E2%80%9CIran's%20membership%20in%20the%20bloc%20is%20opposition%20to%20American%20unilateralism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Needs%20To%20Defines%20Its%20Position%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20China%20share%20this%20sentiment%20of%20BRICS%20emerging%20as%20a%20counterbalance%20to%20the%20West.%20But%20what%20about%20India%3F%20India%20has%20lauded%20and%20endorsed%20Iran's%20presence%20in%20BRICS%2C%20but%20will%20New%20Delhi%20also%20endorse%20Tehran's%20oppressive%20domestic%20policies%20in%20the%20name%20of%20this%20cooperative%20alliance%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20not%20stopped%20buying%20oil%20from%20Iran%20despite%20the%20sanctions%20and%20disapproving%20remarks%20from%20the%20West.%20Yet%2C%20bilateral%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20has%20dropped%20by%2026%25%20in%20one%20year.%20Geoeconomics%20informs%20Iranian%20perceptions%20of%20the%20bloc%20as%20a%20critical%20driver.%20Iran%20aims%20to%20secure%20increased%20volumes%20of%20oil%20and%20non-oil%20exports%20to%20fellow%20BRICS%20members%2C%20bypassing%20the%20dollar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Russia%2C%20Iran%20is%20engaged%20in%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%20with%20the%20West.%20China%20doesn't%20particularly%20enjoy%20a%20friendly%20status%2C%20either.%20New%20Delhi's%20balancing%20act%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20tested%20on%20many%20tricky%20issues%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20including%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20an%20outlier%20in%20a%20manner.%20At%20the%20last%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20vote%20on%20a%20resolution%20calling%20for%20the%20end%20to%20Israel's%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20territories%2C%20India%20was%20the%20only%20founding%20BRICS%20country%20to%20abstain%2C%20along%20with%20the%20newcomer%20Ethiopia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Modi-Pezeshkian%20bilateral%2C%20India%20was%20urged%20to%20play%20a%20more%20substantial%20role%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20peace%20process.%20But%20what%20are%20New%20Delhi's%20realistic%20options%3F%20Calling%20for%20peace%20does%20not%20usher%20in%20peace%3B%20arm-twisting%20the%20stakeholders%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Sticky%20Question%20For%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20BRICS%20decision%20mandates%20unanimous%20agreement.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20it%20is%20even%20trickier%20than%20the%20domestic%20coalition%20politics%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20after%20a%20decade.%20What%20will%2C%20for%20example%2C%20be%20India's%20stand%20should%20Iran%20want%20a%20revival%20of%20its%20nuclear%20plan%3F%20India's%20past%20tussles%20with%20the%20West%20over%20its%20own%20nuclear%20programme%20may%20trigger%20another%20round%20of%20strategic%20unpleasantness%20over%20New%20Delhi's%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20a%20long-standing%20policy%20of%20strategic%20autonomy%2C%20and%20the%20complexity%20of%20its%20relations%20with%20the%20West%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course.%20The%20question%20is%20only%20of%20degree.%20The%20scope%20of%20India's%20support%20to%20its%20alliance%20partners%20in%20any%20overtures%2C%20real%20or%20perceived%2C%20against%20the%20West%20needs%20to%20be%20clearly%20defined%2C%20if%20not%20announced.%20While%20BRICS%20has%20achieved%20precious%20little%20in%20tangible%20terms%20in%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20the%20symbolism%20of%20grouping%20may%20have%20consequences%20for%20India%20as%20ongoing%20conflicts%20stretch%20into%20the%20future%20and%20new%20challenges%20around%20them%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20internal%20dynamics%20of%20the%20expanded%20BRICS%20are%20going%20to%20pose%20another%20challenge.%20BRICS%2C%20only%20a%20little%20more%20than%20an%20ad%20hoc%20grouping%20with%20diverse%20challenges%20and%20interests%2C%20has%20miles%20to%20go%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20counterforce%20to%20alliances%20like%20the%20G7%20or%20the%20Five%20Eyes%2C%20where%20members%20have%20been%20able%20to%20thrash%20out%20at%20least%20a%20common%20minimum%20programme.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-base