%20seat%20for%20India%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20today%20said%20established%20institutions%20must%20be%20reformed%20to%20create%20a%20more%20equitable%20global%20order.%20He%20also%20reiterated%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20message%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war%20and%20global%20disputes%20must%20be%20resolved%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%2016th%20BRICS%20Summit%20in%20Russia's%20Kazan%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBRICS%20is%20a%20statement%20of%20how%20profoundly%20the%20old%20order%20is%20changing.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20many%20inequities%20of%20the%20past%20also%20continue.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20have%20assumed%20new%20forms%20and%20manifestations.%20We%20see%20that%20in%20the%20access%20to%20developmental%20resources%20and%20modern%20technology%20and%20efficiencies.%20Let%20us%20also%20recognise%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20globalisation%20have%20been%20very%20uneven.%20Adding%20to%20all%20that%2C%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20multiple%20conflicts%20have%20aggravated%20the%20burdens%20borne%20by%20the%20Global%20South.%20Concerns%20of%20health%2C%20food%20and%20fuel%20security%20are%20particularly%20acute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20the%20world%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20falling%20significantly%20behind%20in%20realising%20targets%20of%20sustainable%20development%20goals.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20create%20a%20more%20equitable%20global%20order%3F%20First%2C%20by%20strengthening%20and%20expanding%20platforms%20of%20an%20independent%20nature%2C%20and%20by%20widening%20the%20choices%20in%20different%20domains%20and%20minimising%20undue%20reliance%20on%20those%20that%20can%20be%20leveraged.%20This%20is%20really%20where%20BRICS%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20for%20the%20Global%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecond%2C%20by%20reforming%20established%20institutions%20and%20mechanisms%2C%20especially%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20in%20the%20permanent%20and%20the%20non-permanent%20categories.%20So%20too%20the%20multilateral%20development%20banks%2C%20whose%20working%20procedures%20are%20just%20as%20outdated%20as%20that%20of%20the%20UN%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20India%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20initiated%20an%20effort%20in%20this%20direction%20during%20its%20G20%20Presidency%20and%20is%20glad%20to%20see%20Brazil%20take%20it%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20has%20been%20India's%20longstanding%20demand.%20This%20demand%20is%20backed%20by%20major%20world%20powers%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20France.%20Currently%2C%20China%2C%20France%2C%20Russia%2C%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20US%20are%20permanent%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThird%2C%20by%20democratising%20the%20global%20economy%20through%20creating%20more%20production%20hubs.%20The%20Covid%20experience%20is%20a%20sharp%20reminder%20of%20the%20need%20for%20more%20resilient%20and%20shorter%20supply%20chains.%20For%20essential%20needs%2C%20every%20region%20legitimately%20aspires%20to%20create%20their%20own%20production%20capabilities.%20Fourth%2C%20by%20correcting%20distortions%20in%20global%20infrastructure%20that%20are%20a%20legacy%20from%20the%20colonial%20era.%20The%20world%20urgently%20needs%20more%20connectivity%20options%20that%20enhance%20logistics%20and%20mitigate%20risks.%20This%20must%20be%20a%20collective%20endeavour%20for%20the%20common%20good%2C%20with%20the%20utmost%20respect%20for%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty.%20And%20fifth%2C%20by%20sharing%20experiences%20and%20new%20initiatives.%20India's%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%2C%20its%20Unified%20Payment%20Interface%2C%20the%20Gatishakti%20infrastructure%20all%20hold%20a%20larger%20relevance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20added%20that%20the%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%2C%20the%20Coalition%20for%20Disaster%20Resilient%20Infrastructure%2C%20the%20Global%20Biofuel%20Alliance%2C%20Mission%20LiFE%20and%20the%20International%20Big%20Cat%20Alliance%20are%20initiatives%20of%20common%20interest.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20First%20Responder%2C%20be%20it%20for%20natural%20calamities%2C%20health%20emergencies%20or%20economic%20crises%2C%20we%20seek%20to%20do%20our%20fair%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20war%20in%20West%20Asia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20said%20addressing%20conflicts%20effectively%20is%20a%20particular%20need%20of%20the%20day.%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20emphasised%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war.%20Disputes%20and%20differences%20must%20be%20settled%20by%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%20Agreements%2C%20once%20reached%2C%20must%20be%20scrupulously%20respected.%20International%20law%20should%20be%20adhered%20to%2C%20without%20exception.%20And%20there%20should%20be%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20West%20Asia%20for%20us%2C%20is%20an%20understandable%20concern.%20There%20is%20a%20widespread%20anxiety%20that%20the%20conflict%20would%20spread%20further%20in%20the%20region.%20Maritime%20trade%20has%20also%20been%20deeply%20affected.%20The%20human%20and%20material%20consequences%20of%20further%20escalation%20are%20truly%20serious.%20Any%20approach%20has%20to%20be%20fair%20and%20durable%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20two%20state%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20reiterating%20India's%20long-held%20stand%20on%20the%20Palestine%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729764180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F7uisai7o_s-jaishankar-pti_625x300_16_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-calls-fo