Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20inspiring%20stories%20of%20everyday%20Indians%20who%20overcame%20polio%20and%20made%20a%20meaningful%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDr%20Shravan%20Chaudhary%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2010%20months%20old%2C%20Dr%20Shravan%20Chaudhary%20contracted%20polio%2C%20leaving%20him%20unable%20to%20walk.%20A%20resident%20of%20Jaswantpura%20in%20Rajgarh%20tehsil%20of%20Ajmer%2C%20Dr%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20numerous%20hospital%20visits%20during%20his%20childhood%20inspired%20him%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medicine.%20However%2C%20the%20road%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331387%2Finspirational-story-of-rajasthan-doctor-shravan-chaudhary-polio-vaccine-drops-awareness%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disqualified%20from%20appearing%20for%20the%20Pre-Medical%20Test%20(PMT)%20due%20to%20the%2080%20percent%20disability%20in%20my%20lower%20limbs.%20I%20had%20to%20move%20the%20Rajasthan%20High%20Court.%20Through%20their%20intervention%2C%20I%20enrolled%20for%20MBBS.%20After%20five%20years%20of%20devotion%20and%20hard%20work%2C%20I%20became%20a%20doctor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxzC3Wpo7JD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxzC3Wpo7JD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3