nderstand%20the%20hardships%20under%20which%20they%20lived.%20He%20learnt%20that%20local%20communities%20were%20not%20unwilling%20but%20unable%20to%20%E2%80%9Cactually%20participate%20in%20conservation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snow%20Leopard%20(Images%20courtesy%20Karamjeet%20Singh%2FX)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20(Images%20courtesy%20Karamjeet%20Singh%2FX)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkin%20to%20the%20model%20later%20adopted%20by%20the%20late%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368687%2Fworld-animal-welfare-day-remembering-pioneers-wildlife-conservation-india-project-tiger%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERinchen%20Wangchuk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20Charu%20created%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20community-managed%20livestock%20insurance%20programme%20in%202002%20%E2%80%94%20followed%20by%20other%20community-based%20conservation%20and%20livelihood%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20he%20established%20the%20Global%20Snow%20Leopard%20and%20Ecosystem%20Protection%20Programme%2C%20%E2%80%9Can%20intergovernmental%20alliance%20of%20all%2012%20snow%20leopard%20range%20countries%20working%20towards%20their%20protection%E2%80%9D.%20Today%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20impart%20valuable%20knowledge%20to%20other%20conservationists%20on%20how%20to%20ethically%20and%20effectively%20engage%20with%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20snow%20leopards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhitleyaward.org%2Fwinners%2Fbuilding-global-capacity-for-community-led-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERinchen%20Wangchuk%2C%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20and%20Jigmet%20Dadul%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%20from%20Ladakh%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246169%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-saviours-rinchen-wangchuk-tsewang-namgail-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SLC-IT)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20successor%20(current%20director%20of%20SLC-IT)%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20understood%20very%20early%20on%20the%20need%20to%20reconcile%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20local%20communities%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%2C%20particularly%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20to%20these%20elusive%20wild%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20growing%20up%20as%20a%20child%20herder%20in%20the%20picturesque%20Skurbuchan%20village%20in%20Leh%20district%2C%20Dr%20Namgail%20understoo