68w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-239904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhenrab%20Phuntsog%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20conservationists%20have%20stated%20in%20the%20past%2C%20there%20is%20something%20almost%20mythical%20and%20spiritual%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20snow%20leopards.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20Khenrab%20also%20felt%20when%20he%20was%2012%20and%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20this%20vivid%20memory%20he%20had%20of%20a%20snow%20leopard%20would%20inspire%20Khenrab%20to%20dedicate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Department%20in%202000%2C%20he%20has%20rescued%20about%2050%20snow%20leopards%20trapped%20in%20human%20habitations%20and%20released%20them%20back%20into%20the%20wild.%20An%20expert%20in%20installing%20camera%20traps%20and%20tracking%2C%20he%20also%20consults%20private%20operators%20on%20how%20to%20plan%20snow%20leopard%20expeditions%2C%20train%20spotters%20and%20trackers%2C%20and%20leave%20behind%20a%20minimal%20ecological%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264378%2Fkarma-sonam-natwest-group-earth-heroes-award-snow-leopard-himalayan-wolf-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20field%20manager%20with%20the%20Nature%20Conservation%20Foundation%20(NCF)%20in%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20reducing%20human-wildlife%20conflict%20in%2017%20communities%20across%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20creating%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20environmental%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20a%20system%20of%20community-based%20conservation%2C%20he%20has%20facilitated%20the%20implementation%20of%20critical%20initiatives%20like%20self-sustaining%20insurance%20schemes%20for%20pastoralists%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%20to%20predators%20like%20snow%20leopards%2C%20creation%20of%20grazing-free%20reserves%20for%20herbivores%20like%20the%20Tibetan%20gazelle%20(that%20are%20prey%20for%20snow%20leopards)%2C%20and%20converting%20Shandongs%20(traditional%20wolf%20traps)%20into%20holy%20Buddhist%20sites%20that%20allow%20trapped%20animals%20to%20escape%20back%20into%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karma%20Sonam%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011.jpg%20720w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20worked%20for%20Karma%20is%20his%20natural%20ability%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20close%20relationships%20with%20different%20communities.%20Leveraging%20these%20close%20relationships%2C%20he%20convinces%20and%20incentivises%20local%20communities%20to%20work%20for%20wildlife%20conservation.%20For%20decades%2C%20pastoralists%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20had%20a%20difficult%20relationship%20with%20predators%2C%20like%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20who%20prey%20on%20their%20livestock.%20Through%20his%20extensive%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20repair%20that%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-b