es%20is%20that%20not%20a%20single%20penny%20of%20the%20money%20meant%20for%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20goes%20into%20the%20pocket%20of%20the%20snow%20leopards.%20It%20is%20always%20invested%20in%20support%20of%20people%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20local%20or%20indigenous%20communities%20running%20conservation%20programmes%2C%20the%20frontline%20rangers%20patrolling%20and%20monitoring%20wildlife%2C%20or%20the%20conservation%20teams%20working%20under%20expedition%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Koustubh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6our%20initiatives%20are%20about%20much%20more%20than%20just%20protecting%20a%20single%20species.%20We%20work%20closely%20with%20local%20and%20indigenous%20communities%20to%20create%20sustainable%20livelihoods%20that%20benefit%20both%20people%20and%20wildlife.%20When%20we%20invest%20in%20conservation%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20investing%20in%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-koustubh-sharma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanctuary%20Nature%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsnowleopard.org%2Fmeet-snow-leopard-trusts-new-conservation-science-director-dr-koustubh-sharma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShiv%20Kumar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20evening%20in%202019%20when%20Shiv%20Kumar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Deputy%20Range%20Officer%20at%20Lahaul%20forest%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20first%20spotted%20a%20snow%20leopard.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F274641%2Fforest-guard-officer-photographs-snow-leopard-conservation-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_b