0Khanna%E2%80%99s%20primary%20identifier%20is%20that%20of%20a%20proud%20Indian.%20And%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Etadka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spices%20heated%20in%20hot%20oil)%20that%20makes%20its%20way%20into%20his%20curries%20to%20the%20sparkle%20in%20his%20eyes%20when%20he%20speaks%20about%20life%20back%20in%20his%20beloved%20hometown%2C%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20Vikas%20Khanna%2C%20all%20roads%20lead%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanna%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20mind%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20occupy%20it.%20Memories%20of%20serving%20the%20who%E2%80%99s%20who%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20he%20has%20been%20the%20%3Cem%3Echef%20du%20jour%3C%2Fem%3E%20multiple%20times%20for%20the%20Obama%20family%2C%20while%20also%20working%20closely%20with%20food%20mogul%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20%E2%80%94%20find%20space%20right%20next%20to%20nostalgic%20memories%20of%20binge%20sessions%20involving%20rounds%20of%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(potato%20patties)%20from%20%E2%80%98Mathura%20ki%20Tikki%E2%80%99%20in%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Among%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna's%20fondest%20memories%20are%20those%20with%20his%20family%20and%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20his%20hometown%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fv